RACE.FOOTNOTES: SHASTA STAR stalked the top pair early on down the backstretch, raced along the inside around the far turn, angled five wide through the stretch and finished strongly to surge up under strong handling. THREATLEVELMIDNITE (GB) tracked Claire's Darling early on racing just off the inside, took aim into the upper stretch, led near the sixteenth pole but couldn't hold off Shasta Star late in a game effort. VIKING QUEEN raced mid pack early on, ridden along through the far turn, moved up from the inside into the upper stretch, angled and showed good late interest. CLAIRE'S DARLING was sent along from the outside to cross over an set the early pace, was clear near the three sixteenths pole and weakened the final eighth of a mile. FLAVA'S DREAM stumbled at the break, raced off the early pace after the poor start, raced near the inside around the far turn through the stretch and lacked a rally. POLISHED GAL stalked the pace early on, moved up three to four wide around the far turn and flattened out in the drive. EVANGELINE ALLONS dropped back early on, raced five deep into the upper stretch to race outside of foes and lacked a bid. SHEKNOWSTHEDRILL was off a step slow, void of early speed and trailed.
